title: "US51 — Respond with expert advice"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>RequestDetailScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SendDeliverable
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>SupabaseGateway
  A->>B: write advice / attach plan
  B->>C: send(deliverable)
  C->>G: insert deliverables
  G-->>C: ok
  C->>G: update request → completed (CompleteServiceRequest)
  B-->>A: delivered - client sees it under purchases
